      <title>美联储表示基差贸易“显着”小于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/fed-says-basis-trade-significantly-smaller-than-estimated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储研究人员表示，美国国债基差交易（一种引起监管机构审查的债券市场策略）的金额可能只有常用估计值的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/fed-says-basis-trade-significantly-smaller-than-estimated</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
